  "description": "A massive container ship, the \"COSCO FORTUNE\", is docked at a busy port. The ship is heavily laden with colorful shipping containers stacked high, creating a wall of reds, blues, greens, and yellows. A small white tugboat is positioned in front of the ship, seemingly assisting with docking. In the background, more ships and port infrastructure, including cranes, are visible. The water is calm, reflecting the ship and sky. The overall scene conveys a sense of global trade and industrial activity.",
